Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:04.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Più passa il tempo,\N più i casi difficili aumentano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Il caso di oggi è nella villa di un milionario.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,C'è un'ombra oscura\N dietro al candeliere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Riesce a discernere l'unica verità,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,anche se è un bambino, \Nla sua mente è quella di un adulto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:15.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Il suo nome? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:52.08,Titolo episodio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,50)\blur1\bord0.5\c&HDDFEE0&\pos(261,287)}I{\c&HDDFEE0&}l{\c&HDDFEE0&} {\c&HDDFEE1&}c{\c&HDDFEE1&}a{\c&HDDFEE1&}s{\c&HDDFEE1&}o{\c&HDDFDE1&} {\c&HDDFDE1&}d{\c&HDDFDE2&}e{\c&HDDFDE2&}l{\c&HDDFDE2&}l{\c&HDDFDE2&}'{\c&HDDFDE2&}o{\c&HDDFDE3&}m{\c&HDDFDE3&}i{\c&HDDFDE3&}c{\c&HDDFDE3&}i{\c&HDDFDE3&}d{\c&HDDFCE3&}i{\c&HDDFCE4&}o{\c&HDDFCE4&} {\c&HDDFCE4&}d{\c&HDDFCE4&}e{\c&HDDFCE4&}l{\c&HDDFCE5&}l{\c&HDDFCE5&}'{\c&HDDFCE5&}e{\c&HDDFCE5&}r{\c&HDDFCE5&}e{\c&HDDFCE6&}d{\c&HDDFBE6&}i{\c&HDDFBE6&}t{\c&HDDFBE6&}i{\c&HDDFBE6&}e{\c&HDDFBE6&}r{\c&HDDFBE7&}a\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs18\c&HDDFBE7&}({\c&HDDFBE7&}p{\c&HDDFBE7&}r{\c&HDDFBE7&}i{\c&HDDFBE8&}m{\c&HDDFBE8&}a{\c&HDDFAE8&} {\c&HDDFAE8&}p{\c&HDDFAE8&}a{\c&HDDFAE8&}r{\c&HDDFAE9&}t{\c&HDDFAE9&}e{\c&HDDFAE9&})
